      "content": "The Statorium American Football API provides NFL data including live game scores, schedules, player news, team statistics, rosters, and historical records. The API delivers unique daily news feeds linked to NFL players and teams along with game data in JSON format. Coverage includes all NFL teams and games for current and past seasons.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Statorium Support",
